text: Alice Kristina Ingrid Gernandt (born 23 July 1982 in Stockholm), better known by her stage name Ace Wilder, is a Swedish singer and songwriter. She is best known for taking part in Melodifestivalen 2014 were she placed second behind Sanna Nielsen. ==References== Category:Living people Category:1982 births Category:Singers from Stockholm Category:Swedish singer-songwriters Category:Writers from Stockholm Category:Synth-pop singers
